          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "3",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the finest & famed Education Institution (Ranking - among the top 10 schools in India), with historic European (French) architectural building - \"La Martiniere for Girl's\" boasts of a glorious Heritage. The Institute (ICSE board) has dedicatedly enlightened the Calcuttans over the past 186 years. The school management has a strict & diligent vigil over Academics & Discipline, along with other vocational courses & sports activities. The sprawling school campus is one the finest in the city with all amenities. Though this is an Upscale School yet students thrive to get admissions in the elite institution.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
