            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best day schools in India and best in the east. This is a Girl's only school the La Martiniere for Boys has a different campus just 50 meters away from the Girl's block. The school have produced a number of renowned scholars and also business personalities. One of the oldest schools in India.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
